urls.title: Sao Paulo's Best Kept Secrets - Airbnb
urls.description: Centro Histórico de São Paulo - Best way to take a look at one the biggest cities on the planet? From the bottom to the top, of course! We'll be visiting some of the not-so-obvious historical locations that will help you understand the fascinating stories behind the development of Sao Paulo. This tour will put you in context with the reality of my hometown with some social and cultural insights. Other things to note Sao Paulo's Oldtown is like a big maze, so bring your enthusiasm and curiosity! If you want a customized tour or a different time than offered here, just message me and we can talk about it :) About delays: São Paulo is a HUGE city and the traffic can be really unpredictable, so plan your journey to our meeting spot with a bit of extra time to prevent delays; 15 minutes is the tolerance. PLEASE NOTE: Some of the attractions might be unavailable due to weather conditions, maintenance or holidays!
